me.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/mac-miller-2014@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/mac-miller-2014@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/mac-miller-2014@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/mac-miller-2014@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mac-miller">麦克·米勒 (Mac Miller)</a>即将发行的第二张遗作专辑《Balloonerism》的曲目列表已由他的家人公布 - 请在下面查看。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/mac-miller-circles-review-2598177">麦克·米勒 (Mac Miller) – 《Circles》评论：死后专辑是一种相互冲突、诱人的品味。</a></strong></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mac-millers-unreleased-2014-album-balloonerism-will-posthumously-drop-in-early-2025-3814868">去年 11 月</a>，米勒的家人分享说，这位说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/mac-miller-cause-of-death-2397315">在 2018 年因意外服药过量过早去世</a>之前录制的 2014 年专辑，但从未发行过，终于按照他的愿望与公众分享了。</p><p>这张专辑的标题是“Balloonerism”，并且是“一个对马尔科姆来说非常重要的项目——他委托为这张专辑创作艺术作品，并定期讨论该专辑何时发行，尽管最终还是‘GO:OD AM’”随后的专辑最终占据了优先地位。” </p><figure id="attachment_3814869" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3814869" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3814869" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mac-miller@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mac-miller@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mac-miller@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mac-miller@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mac-miller@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mac-miller@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/mac-miller@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3814869" class="wp-caption-text"> Mac Miller 于 2017 年现场表演。图片来源：Rich Fury/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> 《Balloonerism》将于 1 月 17 日上映，距其“在《Faces》发行前后创作”已有 11 年。该专辑<a href="https://www.macmillerswebsite.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">现已开放预购</a>。</p><p>现在，Mac Miller 的家人分享了即将发行的曲目列表，其中包括 SZA 在第二首曲目“DJ&#39;s Chord Organ”中的特色，以及他自己的另一个自我妄想托马斯在歌曲“Transformations”中的罕见亮相。此外，歌曲《5 Dollar Pony Rides》将于今天晚些时候（1 月 9 日）作为专辑的第一首单曲发行。</p><p><strong>请查看下面 Mac Miller 的“Balloonerism”的完整曲目列表：</strong></p><p> <strong>《铃鼓梦》</strong><br /> <strong>“DJ 的和弦风琴” ft. SZA</strong><br /> <strong>《你有目的地吗》</strong><br /> <strong>“5美元骑小马”</strong><br /> <strong>“友好的幻觉”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;太太。黛博拉·唐纳</strong><br /><strong>‘石头’</strong><br /> <strong>“香格里拉”</strong><br /> <strong>“有趣的论文”</strong><br /> <strong>&#39;精益求精&#39;</strong><br /> <strong>《转变》ft.妄想托马斯</strong><br /><strong>“侏儒鸟”</strong><br /> <strong>《瑞克的钢琴》</strong><br /> <strong>“明天永远不会知道”</strong> </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DEiC91Evx9C/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: